query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(kt t mk) NoMergeJoin(kt mk t mi_idx) NoMergeJoin(k kt mi mi_idx mk t it1) NoMergeJoin(it1 k kt mi mi_idx mk t it2) */ select min(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
min(t.title) AS northern_dark_movie
from kind_type AS kt
inner join title AS t
on kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'episode' AND t.production_year > 2008
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on t.id = mk.movie_id
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.info < '6.2'
inner join keyword AS k
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder-in-title',
'female-nudity',
'hospital',
'hitting-on-girl')
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Swedish',
'America',
'Danish',
'German',
'Sweden',
'Bulgaria',
'USA',
'English',
'Germany',
'USA')
inner join info_type AS it1
on it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries'
inner join info_type AS it2
on it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating';
